        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1896441560" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16652825925979519812">A nuanced reflection on race, trauma, and belonging that brings together text and image in unsettling, powerful ways. It’s rare to come across art, least of all poetry, that so obviously will endure the passing of time and be considered over and over, by many.</span>

          </span>
