<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/33375618-don-t-call-us-dead"><img alt="Don&#39;t Call Us Dead" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1485966636l/33375618._SX98_.jpg" />
